More ideas about that.

00:25:43.953 --> 00:25:45.223
Yeah.

00:25:45.223 --> 00:25:48.535
The second-born benefits
from the tutelage

00:25:48.535 --> 00:25:50.220
of the firstborn early in life.

00:25:50.220 --> 00:25:54.144
But later on, having the
