00:27:19.120 --> 00:27:21.765
expensive for the
same parental income.

00:27:21.765 --> 00:27:24.070
And you have got less
to spread to each child.

00:27:24.070 --> 00:27:27.450
So they controlled for that,
looking at within family

00:27:27.450 --> 00:27:29.370
