00:30:56.570 --> 00:30:58.642
monogamous, and
some are polygamous.

00:30:58.642 --> 00:31:00.100
This appears to be
a frequent theme

00:31:00.100 --> 00:31:01.770
in these little rodent things.

00:31:01.770 --> 00:31:04.020
And with the deer
mice, what you find

00:31:04.020 --> 00:31:07.310
is, with the polygamous
