00:31:39.500 --> 00:31:41.270
on sexual competition.

00:31:41.270 --> 00:31:42.442
Sperm competition.

00:31:42.442 --> 00:31:44.400
And there's even hints
that something like that

00:31:44.400 --> 00:31:45.310
